column4: This picture is called "Plaid Pumpkin Polka Dots". The print unframed measures 12x18 inches. The frame will add about one more inch per side. Beautiful print with multiple frame selections to choose from. This fun fall print has a black and white polka dot border around a orange and white gingham background with a simple orange pumpkin and the words, "Hey There, Pumpkin."  Choose your lath frame color to customize your product. All frames have a vintage wire along the top of the frame for quick and easy wall hanging.
